<plot>Bio-Pic of The Great One!, GRETA GARBO, and her on-again / off-again relationships with stars of her era, such as MARLENE DIETRICH. A narrow focus on the greatest actress in the history of film, the woman behind the camera, revealing who she was - a person before her time, living a life dedicated to personal freedom and independence to the confusion of all concerned. An emotionally complicated, individualistic, and self-contained personality is re-vealed through Greta's personal triangle with screenwriter Mercedes DE Acosta and VOGUE photographer/designer Cecil Beaton.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?210123</url></doc>
